%F A129467 Row polynomials p(n,x):= p(n,v=n,x) with the recurrence: p(n,v,x) = (x+2*(n-1)^2-2*(v-1)*(n-1)-v+1)*p(n-1,v,x) -((n-1)^2)*((n-1-v)^2)*p(n-2,v,x)) with p(-1,v,x)=0 and p(0,v,x)=1.
%F A129467 a(n,m)=[x^m] p(n,n,x), n>=m>=0, else 0.
